                    858 Coal Creek Circle
                    Louisville, Colorado 80027
                    U.S.A.
            Phone:  +1 303-661-9100
            Fax:    +1 303-661-9199
            E-mail: mibs@cablelabs.com"

    DESCRIPTION
            "This MIB module supplies the basic management objects 
            for event reporting
            
            Acknowledgements:
              Eugene Nechamkin       -  Broadcom Corp
              John Berg              - CableLabs, Inc.
